title: 2Be Nourished
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Ovo, Western, Juice bar, Take-out
description: A nutrition bar serving salads, wraps, chia pudding, protein balls, slow pressed juices, smoothies with almond or coconut milk. Allergy friendly: gluten free, peanut free, dairy free, and refined sugar free. Has a whole food grocery section sellling some health food and skin care products. Open since Apr 2015.
